	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator? He is cited by his son, an interlocutor in Cic. ND, regarding a session of the Senate in 162 and the double sun in 129 (2.11 and 14, and notes in Pease's edition). Probably a senator (RS, MS-RP 1.283-284, against Münzer, RE no. 18)." .
